</li></ul></div></div></div><div class="sc-iqseJM ducrfW pf-61_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-fHeRUh cCunWv pf-62_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading2" class="sc-bTfYFJ fFWOZc pf-63_ pf-heading-1-h3">Recommendations for businesses and individuals</h3><p class="sc-kHOZwM oQMan pf-65_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3">All businesses, particularly those in high-traffic areas, should consider equipping their premises with an AED. Staff training is equally vital to ensure their confidence in using the device. Individuals, too, are encouraged to familiarise themselves with AED locations in their communities and undergo basic training.





















